{"tid":1860894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫管局：「昨日超過2700名醫護人員缺勤」","createTime":"2020-02-04T02:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T05:28:38.000Z","uid":192941,"like":737,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"4282b4900d1ea81f828d46b80691e72c62153c2f","tid":1860894,"uid":192941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:20:30.000Z","msg":"「昨日超過2700名醫護人員缺勤，雖然公立醫院早前已調整了服務量，盡力確保緊急服務不受影響，其中普通科門診的診症名額已減少了約四分一，而其他非緊急服務和專職醫療服務亦減少了約一半，部分病人的疹症安排、治療程序及預約手術亦需要押後。」<br />\n<br />\n服務受影響比較嚴重的<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">包括個別醫院的新生嬰兒深切治癒部、加護病房、心胸外科、隔離病房、急症科病房。另外，部分醫院的癌症治療、通波仔及放射診斷服務亦彩到不同程度的影響</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n即是琴日係有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">超過9成</span></span>承諾罷工嘅ha員工罷工，同樣地，只要呢幾日大家團結，一定揸住政府春袋，ha亦冇辦法清算到近萬名罷工嘅員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0be520f62fc5c0fcb82e0f01575241c970f6c7b","tid":1860894,"uid":192941,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:21:36.000Z","msg":"HAEA加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538108d6b6b68f95bf83914de2eb5521a40afffe","tid":1860894,"uid":192941,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:22:03.000Z","msg":"HKEA加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a30959e6a67ed06d9e340624784f261a4fb19f6","tid":1860894,"uid":50889,"like":109,"dislike":0,"score":109,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:22:22.000Z","msg":"寫稿條友仲特登將<span style=\"color: red;\">新生嬰兒深切治癒部</span>擺最頭<br />\n攻心到"},{"pid":"5ec5da2bb197b4743f13bfcc8f6149798066b4cf","tid":1860894,"uid":165840,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tong